---
layout: layouts/home
---
{% import 'components/atoms/button.njk' as button %}


<header>
    <h1>Danny de Vries</h1>
    <h2 class="d-1">is a <strong>Lecturer</strong> and <strong>UX engineer.</strong></h2>
    <p> Hi! I'm building digital products trough my design practice <a href="#">Studio Title</a> and tinkering with code on <a href="#">digital projects</a> on the side. I also work as a lecturer at the <a href="https://www.amsterdamuas.com/">Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences</a> where I lecture about code in the technical courses of <a href="https://www.cmd-amsterdam.nl/english/">our program</a> such as <a href="https://github.com/cmda-bt">front-end and back-end.</a></p>
    {{ button.primary('/about', 'More words >')}}
</header>

<main>

<section class="home">
  <section class="article-list c-2">
  {%- for article in collections.article | reverse | limit(3) -%}
    {% include 'components/atoms/article.njk' %}
  {%- endfor -%}
  <a class="article-item" href="/writing">See all writing →</a>
</section>
</section>

<section class="home bg cont">
  <h3 class="p">Speaking</h3>
  <p class="p">I'd like to talk about tech, building for the web and tinkering with code. Some of my talks are technical with code examples. I can give these at your conference or within office hours at your company or meet-up.</p>
  {{ button.primary('/speaking', 'All talks')}}
  {{ button.secondary('/about', 'Events')}}
</section>

<section class="home cont">
<h3>Projects</h3>
  {% import 'components/atoms/card.njk' as card %}

{%- for project in collections.project | limit(3) -%}
  {{ card.item
    (
      project.url,
      project.data.image,
      project.data.title,
      project.data.description
    )
  }}
{%- endfor -%}
<a class="article-item" href="/projects">See all projects →</a>
</section>

<section class="home bg cont">
  <h3 class="p">Teaching</h3>
  <p class="p">An overview of workshops I can give at your conference or office and courses from the Amsterdam University of Applied Sciences. I've also made some online courses to learn with me on the web.</p>
  {{ button.primary('/teaching', 'All courses')}}
  {{ button.secondary('/teaching', 'Workshops')}}
</section>

<section class="blocks">
  {{ card.block("Coaching", "Looking for a mentor to give guidance? Maybe a coaching session or just some quick feedback?", "/coaching", "Read about coaching") }}
  {{ card.block("Support", "If you like my speaking, writing, courses and projects, you can consider supporting me.", "/support", "Support me") }}
  {{ card.block("Contact", "Feel free to contact me if you have any questions. You can e-mail, chat or follow me on social.", "/contact", "Get in touch") }}
</section>
</main>
